unnormalised: Arre yaar, kiteak lagin 10/10/2024-ak poilim korun haddtaat? Mhaka dislem tem 11/11/24-ak tharailam mhunn, tem zaituch shubh!
normalised: Oh nā, kiteāk lagna dha october don hājār chovisāk mukhar dhavarpachem? Mhaka dislem tem egarā november don hājār chovisāk tharāil'lem, jem bhovuch shubh āsa!
text: Arre yaar, kiteak lagin 10/10/2024-ak poilim korun haddtaat? Mhaka dislem tem 11/11/24-ak tharailam mhunn, tem zaituch shubh!
